name: 菅牧典(Kudamaki Tsukasa)/東方Project(Touhou Project)
description:
Kudamaki Tsukasa from touhou 18 Unconnected Marketeers. (v2.0)

Re-trained with better training data, and simpler Danbooru-style tags.

It will work quite differently from the last version, with more stabilized details and her tail.

Megumu and Chimata's lora has also been updated to v2.0, please check it if you're using it!

※ Trigger words (Changed!):

Kudamaki Tsukasa,

fox ears,

fox tail,

hair between eyes,

white romper,

green ribbon,

white socks

※ No necessary Negatives, but adding long hair to a negative can make her hair more stable.

※ You may also add holding test tube to a negative, if cylinder in her hand appeared unexpectedly.

It can also be used as a trigger, but won't work that well.

※ Recommended weight: 0.75~0.9, CFG Scale: 5~7

(Not always the best, better try adjusting from this and find the best condition for your model.)

※ Clip skip: 2

※ Trained with animefull
